block_list.title: Video Tutorial
block_list.body: This marvelous origami plane is the Laser-Jet designed by Thay Yang. It looks really cool with a blade nose. This origami jet could really fly. I hope' you will enjoy it. Enjoy! If you missed my last Exotic Paper Airplane "Paper Plane 045 : Space Shuttle by Gery Hsu", you could watch it at https://youtu.be/saa6NSavwW4 Thanks For Watching! Wilson Lee @Heap Art
